      • append

        public void append(Exec.ExecResult exr)
        "Appends" another Exec.ExecResult to this one.

        Used in order to describe the result of executing a sequence of commands, each having its own Exec.ExecResult.

        Stdout and stderr are appended. The exit error code is overwritten by each append.
        Parameters:
        exr -
